	rch at door. Arrive early. No weapons. www.stgpresents.org/about/safety Th
	is is a general admission event. The ADA section on the seating map does n
	ot represent a specific seat location. When purchasing ADA accessible seat
	ing\, please feel free to contact us by email if assistance is needed with
	 accommodations or companion seating\; you may reach us at accessibility@s
	tgpresents.org. Each accessible seat houses an armless freestanding chair 
